WHO, HOW &amp; WHEN TO SHORT 

If like me you think we’ll get a pull back but also see the Puts on the SPY are very expensive consider Puts on the higher quality tech stocks which have mooned lately;

FB, MSFT, EBAY, ROP, CRM, INTU, DOCU etc Puts are way cheaper with much lower IV.  On top of that and as a hedge in case it keeps pumping the Calls in the SPY are actually very cheap vs the Puts.
